---
title: Chicken, Mushroom & Mozz Hoagies with Dijon Mayo & Seasoned Potato Wedges
description: This week, a classic sandwich gets a veggie-centric twist. Meaty mushrooms are sautéed with bold and savory steak spices til they’re crispy and caramelized. Then, they’re stuffed into toasted baguettes, along with a creamy Dijon mayo, a tangle of peppers and onions, and a blanket of gooey mozz. Add savory potato wedges and you’ve got a restaurant-style meal!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64aedbb0bf53a3eb58aab66a-af420cd3.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/64aedbb0bf53a3eb58aab66a.pdf
servings: 2
cuisine: North America
time required: 35 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 1190 kcal
  fat: 55 g
  saturated fat: 13 g
  carbohydrates: 115 g
  sugar: 15 g
  protein: 51 g
  fiber: 7 g
  sodium: 1430 mg
